        "heading": "10. Referral Criteria",
        "locator": "pages 19–21",
        "evidence_summary": "Defines urgent and specialist review for severe or night pain, infection, trauma, neurological deficit, urinary or faecal dysfunction, systemic disease, persistent symptoms, and selected imaging needs."
